
##  do this AFTER webmin since webmin seems to be very "picky" as to what version it is willing to accept.
## or php upgrade to 7.4 AFTER webmin install??  (could be dangerous)

###  centos-8:

    dnf install https://dl.fedoraproject.org/pub/epel/epel-release-latest-8.noarch.rpm

###to ***UPDATE**** from 7.2 (virtualim favorite version) to 7.4:  (2021-06-24)

  dnf  module  reset php    ;
  dnf module enable  php:7.4   ;
  dnf  update  php\*    ;

